// ЕДИНСТВЕННЫЙ И ПРЕЦИЗИОННЫЙ ЭКЗЕМПЛЯР ФУНКЦИИ ВЫВОДА ПОЛЗУНКОВ (ЗАЩИТА ОТ REDEFINITION)
String makeSliderCard(String name, String range, String id, float currentVal, float min, float max, float step) {
  String card = "    <div class='prot-card'>";
  card += "      <div class='prot-info'><span class='prot-name'>" + name + "</span><span class='prot-range'>" + range + "</span></div>";
  card += "      <input type='range' id='" + id + "' min='" + String(min,0) + "' max='" + String(max,0) + "' step='" + String(step,1) + "' value='" + String(currentVal, (step==1.0f?0:1)) + "' class='hitech-slider' oninput='linkSl(\"" + id + "\",this.value)'>";
  card += "      <input type='text' id='" + id + "-in' value='" + String(currentVal, (step==1.0f?0:1)) + "' class='hitech-input' onchange='linkSl(\"" + id + "\",this.value)'>";
  card += "    </div>";
  return card;
}

